", "createdAt": "2025-03-17T07:17:47-07:00", "path": "/p/agbr/apps-that-push-you-to-create", "title": "Apps that push you to create?", "descriptionPreview": "<p>Last week, I downloaded and purchased @AgBr after seeing it on the homepage. Its design and super specific goal just immediately clicked with me. I love black &amp; white photography, and this was a really interesting and approachable way to experiment with it; even though I've never been much of a photographer myself. I'm usually just appreciating others' photos.</p><p>But then, over this past weekend, I noticed that I kept feeling compelled to take pictures throughout my day so that I could play around with different filters and try out different levels of film grain on them. Having the tools to create was suddenly making me look for more and more opportunities to use them.</p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "294167", "name": "Jake Crump", "username": "jakecrump", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/294167/original.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": true, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": {"id": "112572", "name": "Product Hunt", "slug": "producthunt", "logoUuid": "d618ea86-70ae-4d12-8ec2-0ed78c723ddf.png", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "__typename": "Product"}, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 33, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 13, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "461907", "slug": "agbr", "subject": {"id": "1043537", "name": "AgBr", "logoUuid": "251e98db-cfdd-46cb-a04f-ae2af5dc0160.png", "__typename": "Product"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "104314", "pageViewsCount": 185, "slug": "which-application-do-you-most-often-use-for-photo-editing", "createdAt": "2021-07-18T00:00:00-07:00", "path": "/p/general/which-application-do-you-most-often-use-for-photo-editing", "title": "Which ap